<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 隸屬美國陸軍第三旅的225名士兵、15輛M1主戰坦克及6輛M2步兵戰車經鐵路抵達拉脫維亞北部邊境城市加卡爾尼斯，參與北約針對俄羅斯的「大西洋決心行動」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170210/00180_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170210%2F00180_001.html&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a87e157d\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170210/00180_001.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 英國國會下議院三讀通過首相文翠珊提出的啓動「脫歐」議案，並授權執政保守黨政府啟動《里斯本條約》第50條，與歐盟展開脫歐談判。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170210/00180_009.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170210%2F00180_009.html&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a55358cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170210/00180_009.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1547217&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1547217%26target%3D2&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=25ae6db2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1547217%26target%3D2&h=dcda70e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1547217&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 美國三藩市有關政府部門批准該市唐人街在今年9月設置慰安婦少女像及立碑講述二戰日軍暴行。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170210/00180_011.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170210%2F00180_011.html&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=8a7da66d\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20